Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:06.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:12.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:24.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:43.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:49.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.24,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:05.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:27.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:33.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:44.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:08.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:16.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:27.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:32.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:44.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:48.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:56.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是重要的人柱候补
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果身体垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让我头痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人柱到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底想让我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你们在做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用这个国家和所有的国民制造巨大的炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过方向对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不协助的话就把那个村子消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从拉斯多那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们不对那个村子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助我们毁灭所有国民？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不协助我们让那个村子的人被消灭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃小就能拯救大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微想想就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这才是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起理论 感情为先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我杀死的男人也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成那家伙的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就没法出手 让逆转的机会逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太容易钻空子真是太方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类居然让你这么费劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让斯卡逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连库拉多尼也被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不否认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有点开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活了六十年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在站在国家的顶点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都如父亲大人预计的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有外国来的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连老谋深算的我们也被耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定年轻人的时代已经不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯 你和人类接触的时间太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了我们是怎样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那些叛逆的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不向父亲大人报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从宪兵队的情报来分析 已经知道大致的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐 你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停住 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别刺激他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的目标是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳 要离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在肚子里还养了怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把周围的东西都吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然造出了这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 好不容易抓住的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的生命优先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他记住了我们的脸和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有放他活着回去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把火焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你给我办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的目标可是大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃进那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 居然在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德他们还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能死在这种乱七八糟的战斗里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊·马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被诱饵骗到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来相当生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点回去 你这没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉坐这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我灰溜溜地逃回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下会碍手碍脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的派不上用场 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个呆子大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 去干你该干的活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队的领袖是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是能放着不管的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是布拉德雷大总统？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个话题等会再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经满员了吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能把小孩子留在战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的战斗对手是军队高层吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得从库拉多尼口中探出情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们留在这里和他战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和是不是小孩子没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次提出作战的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助我们到这份上 真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个带上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道用法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是杀人的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是保护你们生命的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手不是杀人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样是会早死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊·马斯坦古在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把拉斯多…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格也全变了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能抓住它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是水蚤草履虫小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来回收库拉多尼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和小不点打架…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么话题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才两次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第五研究所的地下说了五次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那针对某件事情的记忆力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人费神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现马斯坦古了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯多的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞 吞 把他吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也感觉到气息了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有几个人？人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和拉斯对砍的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是清国皇帝第十二子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吞他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不能对我们兄弟出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟 那边拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和拉斯不相上下的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 杰利姆的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被评为班上第一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你写进作文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我能读读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的话就太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲是亚美斯多利斯国的大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个国家拚命干活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲心中所想的一直是这个国家的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了大家能和平地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在解决很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不论多忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也不会忘记家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他爱着我 爱着母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的话 父亲一直都会侧耳倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的愿望 父亲一直会认真地听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 杰利姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们人类没法做到这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你是想被绞死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是想被咬死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说被砍死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 那么就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用攻击眼睛这种下三滥的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小时候就一直在防范暗杀的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯规的技术也不得不学习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能乖乖被抓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要长生不老的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想被折磨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人类别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别小看人类 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能吃你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃刚才的细线眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 不能让他把人柱吞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把哥哥吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 已经吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的 这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有老婆和孩子用过的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开灯太多会让邻居怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我的床上忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去少主身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身体能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那么直接去司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁这机会区分一下己方和敌方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的伤还没好呢 还想再乱来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统也许是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间慢慢等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把孩子们留在战场上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为大人怎么树立榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 被大佐当成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果爱德华君听到了也许会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是照搬了你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 让我很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐居然会走这大胆的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是从周边开始入手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够理解你和支持你的人 能多一个就多一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点迟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算听从他的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是光荣之门还是魔窟的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能受命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定会回来的 你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 祝您好运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是罗伊·马斯坦古吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才妻子给我打电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到任以来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太过繁忙没能到访
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日又是深夜造访非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说古拉曼那狡猾老头还精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就11连败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是12
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你还是下得不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是意识到胜利之后下得太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说我太天真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 不能完全舍弃感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雷文一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央的雷文将军？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很优秀 但是对感情很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经亲自去救负伤的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打乱了阵容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子有多少棋子都不够用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居 居然如此侮辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是因为拯救部下的决心而被中央赏识
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才到中央任职
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可没有被边境的老头说三道四的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这句话惹您生气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明将军还是正义之士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事都可以和您商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拉曼中将这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被那狐狸摆了一道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到会议的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去会议室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经习惯中央都市了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 虽然想和市民多多交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市井的传闻也不能忽视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数是无足轻重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡给猫喂食什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的人出现了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统是人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 没有搞笑细胞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是古拉曼的部下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那方面没有学到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是那种小传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能成为大家茶余饭后的话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这种人进这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 刚才的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统是人造人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是人造人所以怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队里不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说军队有危机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是指军队本身有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这里是地狱深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找消失的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由于惧怕孤独吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使不见身影也不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.12,0:24:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第25话 黑暗之门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这姿态
